<% if signed_in? %>

	<h3>We've created a custom profile based on your answers.</h3>
	<p>Extra explanation can go here, particularly if it helps make the demo more cohesive. We can also just put the profile itself on this page, but I thought an interstitial page like this one would make a better story.</p>
	<%= link_to "View Profile", current_user, class: "btn btn-large btn-primary" %>
